This is a great cover of Laika, originally by Wil Wagner of The Smith Street Band on his solo album Laika.

Georgia Maq is an incredible artist, check out her 7" "With a Q".
https://jackknifemusic.bandcamp.com/album/georgia-maq-with-a-q-7

This is my first tab, but as far as i can tell this seems accurate, here's the video to compare:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WKGA9VISmBQ 

Strumming pattern is easy to pick up from the video.  Georgia uses some variations on the D chord every now and
then using her pinkie, but it's not necessarily required to sound good.

Enjoy.

CAPO 5
